OL,3,CMinimum wage to rise in Guernsey from
OL,4,COctober
OL,6,FThe minimum wage for adults in
OL,7,FGuernsey will rise from October after
OL,8,Fpoliticians voted to up the amount
OL,9,Femployers have to pay.
OL,11,FWorkers will be given at least #12 per
OL,12,Fhour instead of the current #10.65.
OL,14,FSome politicians unsuccessfully argued
OL,15,Fthis was too high as they believe it
OL,16,Fwill put too much pressure on
OL,17,Fbusinesses, ultimately leading to
OL,18,Fhigher prices for consumers amid
OL,19,Fongoing cost of living pressures.
